name: An Artist of the Floating World

metadata.name: The World Is Funny
metadata.description:
"Either I’m funny or the world’s funny. I don’t know which. The bottle and lid don’t fit. It could be the bottle’s fault or the lid’s fault. In either case, there’s no denying that the fit is bad."


This analog collage was made with found photos, expressing how our memories can be distorced to fit a fun world, but in the end we should question ourselves if it really is.

First buyer will receive the unframed original artwork. Secondary buyers will receive a signed print.
